- set_meta_tags title: t('.title')
h1.text-center.mt-4 = t('.title')
.container
  .row
    .col-md-10.offset-md-1.col-lg-8.offset-lg-2
      = form_with model: @user, url: password_reset_path(@token), local: true do |f|
        .form-group
          = f.label :email, class: 'w-100'
          = @user.email
        .form-group
          = f.label :password
          = f.password_field :password, class: 'form-control', required: true
          small.form-text.text-muted 半角英小文字・英大文字・数字を組み合わせ、8文字以上で入力してください。
        .form-group
          = f.label :password_confirmation
          = f.password_field :password_confirmation, class: 'form-control', required: true
        .form-group.text-center
          = f.submit t('defaults.register'), class: 'btn btn-primary'
